<%= provide(:body_id, 'param-setting') %>
<%= provide(:result, '系统说明') %>

<div class="container-fluid content-wrapper">
  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <div class="hero-unit">
        <button type="button" class="close hidden-phone" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
        <h1>关联出口数据</h1>

        <div class="row-fluid hidden-desktop hidden-phone">
          <div class="span12">
            <p>
              将用户与出口进行关联，从而使之可以察看相关的工单报表。<br/>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p></p>


        <p class="hidden-phone">
          <a class="btn btn-info btn-large pull-right">详细指南请猛击此处 &raquo;</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
     <div class="span12">
       <ul class="breadcrumb">
         <li>
           <a href="/">
             <i class="radmin-icon radmin-home"></i>
             首页
           </a>
           <span class="divider">/</span>
         </li>
         <li>
           <a href="mng_user">
             <i class="radmin-icon radmin-file"></i>
             管理系统用户
           </a>
           <span class="divider">/</span>
         </li>
         <li class="active">
           <i class="radmin-icon radmin-file"></i>
           关联出口数据
         </li>
       </ul>
     </div>
   </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <div class="row-fluid hidden-desktop hidden-phone">
        <form class="form-vertical " action="p_interaction" method="get">
          <div class="span6">
            <h4 class="title">所有未关联的出口</h4>

            <div class="squiggly-border"></div>
            <div class="well">
              <fieldset>

                <div class="control-group">
                  <label class="control-label" for="optionsCheckboxList">出口名称如下示：</label>

                  <div class="controls">
                    <% @en.each do |n| %>
                      <label class="checkbox">
                        <input type="checkbox" value="<%= n.id %>" name="excblist[]">
                        <%= n.alias %> - <%= n.name %>
                      </label>
                    <% end %>
                    <p class="help-block">
                      <strong>注意:</strong>
                      此处只显示那些尚未有关联的出口，如果需要修改，请先删除原有关联信息。
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>

              </fieldset>
            </div>

          </div>
          <div class="span6">
            <h4 class="title">用户信息</h4>

            <div class="squiggly-border"></div>
            <div class="well">
              <fieldset>
                <div class="control-group">
                  <label class="control-label" for="optionsCheckboxList">用户信息如下示：</label>

                  <div class="controls">
                    <% @users.each do |u| %>
                      <label class="radio">
                        <input type="radio" value="<%= u.id %>" name="uid">
                        <%= u.uname %>(<%= u.alias %>)
                      </label>
                    <% end %>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </fieldset>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button class="btn btn-large btn-info span4 offset4" type="submit">提 交</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <h4 class="title">名言警句</h4>

      <div class="squiggly-border"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <blockquote>
        <p>
          当一切似乎毫无希望时，我看着切石工人在他的石头上，敲击了上百次，而不见任何裂痕出现。
          但在第一百零一次时，石头被劈成两半。我体会到，并非那一击，而是前面的敲打使它裂开。
        </p>
        <small class="pull-right">贾柯·瑞斯</small>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>